[
  {
    "startTime": 5.84,
    "endTime": 9.29,
    "text": "Hi Bob the Canadian here and I just wanted to talk to you a little bit about a phrase"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.39,
    "endTime": 15.279,
    "text": "or question that you hear quite often in everyday speech and that question is, \"How is it going?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.279,
    "endTime": 16.28,
    "text": "Now we're a little unfair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.28,
    "endTime": 19.130000000000003,
    "text": "Uh, in everyday speech we don't speak that slowly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.13,
    "endTime": 24.46,
    "text": "Uh, we don't normally greet each other by pronouncing and enunciating each word correctly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.26,
    "endTime": 28.700000000000003,
    "text": "We don't walk up and say, \"How is it going Dave?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.0,
    "endTime": 30.349,
    "text": "\"It is going fine Bob.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.349,
    "endTime": 32.88,
    "text": "Uh, but we normally start to compress things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.78,
    "endTime": 38.39,
    "text": "So the question, \"How is it going?\", the first compression down sounds a little more like this,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.39,
    "endTime": 42.46,
    "text": "\"How's it goin?\"."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.16,
    "endTime": 48.87,
    "text": "So we take the \"How is\", and it becomes, \"How's\", and we take the \"going\" at the end"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.87,
    "endTime": 50.717999999999996,
    "text": "and it becomes, \"goin\"."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.619,
    "endTime": 51.92,
    "text": "We kind of drop the \"g\" off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.72,
    "endTime": 55.58,
    "text": "So we say, \"How's it goin?\"."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.58,
    "endTime": 57.719,
    "text": "How's it goin?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.719,
    "endTime": 59.799,
    "text": "Then we get even faster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.799,
    "endTime": 62.92,
    "text": "So you'll hear people say things like, \"Howzitgoin?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.92,
    "endTime": 63.92,
    "text": "Howzitgoin?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.92,
    "endTime": 64.92,
    "text": "Howzitgoin?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.72,
    "endTime": 65.92,
    "text": "Howzitgoin?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.92,
    "endTime": 69.09,
    "text": "Uh, where they compress the entire phrase down into one word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.09,
    "endTime": 69.909,
    "text": "Howzitgoin?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.909,
    "endTime": 71.43,
    "text": "Howzitgoin?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.33,
    "endTime": 74.64999999999999,
    "text": "Typical responses to, \"Howzitgoin?\" would be:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.65,
    "endTime": 76.32000000000001,
    "text": "It's going fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.42,
    "endTime": 77.42,
    "text": "It is going fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.42,
    "endTime": 78.60000000000001,
    "text": "It's going fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.7,
    "endTime": 79.5,
    "text": "It's fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.6,
    "endTime": 79.89999999999999,
    "text": "Or"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.1,
    "endTime": 82.19999999999999,
    "text": "It's going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.3,
    "endTime": 81.7,
    "text": "It's going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.8,
    "endTime": 82.8,
    "text": "Howzitgoin?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.9,
    "endTime": 84.2,
    "text": "It's going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.3,
    "endTime": 85.39999999999999,
    "text": "How's it going with you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.4,
    "endTime": 85.9,
    "text": "It's going."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.9,
    "endTime": 86.4,
    "text": "It's ok."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.4,
    "endTime": 91.2,
    "text": "Um, so again, that's the question, \"How is it going?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.2,
    "endTime": 94.7,
    "text": "So listen for that when you hear English speakers speaking a little more rapidly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.7,
    "endTime": 96.36,
    "text": "How's it going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.36,
    "endTime": 97.36,
    "text": "Thanks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.36,
    "endTime": 98.36,
    "text": "Bob the Canadian here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.36,
    "endTime": 99.57,
    "text": "Learn English with Bob the Canadian."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.57,
    "endTime": 100.928,
    "text": "Don't forget to subscribe."
  }
